import './Blast.css' import axios from 'axios' import { useForm } from 'react-hook-form' import {useEffect, useState} from 'react' import {type} from '@testing-library/user-event/dist/type' const sendRequest = (data, service) => { axios.post(`http://192.168.1.37:8080/services/${service}`, data, { headers: { "Content-type":"multipart/form-data" } }) .then() .catch() } const Blast = () => { const {register, handleSubmit} = useForm() const [databases, getDatabases] = useState() const getBlastDb = () => { axios.get(`http://192.168.1.37:8080/db/blast-db`).then(res => { getDatabases(res.data.map(entry => { return })) }) } useEffect(getBlastDb, []) return (
sendRequest(data,'blast')) }>
) } const blastDb = () => { const {register, handleSubmit} = useForm() return (
sendRequest(data, 'blast-db'))}>
) } export default Blast
